summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Agnes B. Sherman, a widow, to the City of Seattle; from the Estate of Peter Olson, deceased, late of Brinnon, Washington, by Anna Olson, Executrix of the last will and testament of said decedent, and Anna Olson, individually for herself, his widow, to the City of Seattle; from H.L. Carpenter and Mary V. Carpenter, his wife, to the City of Seattle; and from Lucy Emmons, to the City of Seattle, and laying off 5th Avenue North.
